                                Rooms
                            </p>
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="h-11 text-stone-500 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:text-stone-800 transition"
                                viewBox="0 0 512 512">
                                <path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="48" d="M184 112l144 144-144 144" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <ul
                            class="overflow-hidden flex flex-col gap-4 max-h-0 max-w-0 border-t-2 border-stone-500 rounded-b-sm lg:bg-amber-100 lg:absolute lg:bottom-0 lg:translate-y-full group-hover:max-h-fit group-hover:max-w-fit group-hover:px-2 group-hover:py-4 ease-in-out duration-100 lg:gap-4 group-hover:lg:px-4 group-hover:lg:py-6">
                            <li>
                                <a href="/rooms/genorals-quarters"
                                    class="text-3xl text-stone-500 font-bold hover:text-stone-800 transition lg:text-2xl">General's
                                    Quarters</a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a href="/rooms/majors-suite"
                                    class="text-3xl text-stone-500 font-bold hover:text-stone-800 transition lg:text-2xl">Major's
                                    Suite</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/contact"
                            class="text-3xl text-stone-500 font-bold hover:text-stone-800 transition lg:text-2xl">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="h-fit flex justify-center py-2 order-first lg:order-last">
